          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/18801281-off-season">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2272883-melissa?shelf=horror">horror</a>, 
